text: Mouilleron-Saint-Germain is a commune. It is found in the region Pays de la Loire in the Vendée department in the west of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Mouilleron- en-Pareds (the seat) and Saint-Germain-l'Aiguiller.Arrêté préfectoral 19 November 2015 == Related pages == * Communes of the Vendée department == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Vendée
title: Mouilleron-Saint-Germain
